\hypertarget{appendix-e-phase-2-e2-bundle-diagnostics-optional}{%
\subsection{Appendix E: Phase-2 E2 bundle diagnostics
(optional)}\label{appendix-e-phase-2-e2-bundle-diagnostics-optional}}

This optional appendix is included only when the build defines
\texttt{\textbackslash GSCWITHPHASE2E2} (for example via
\texttt{build\_paper.sh --phase2-e2-bundle ...}). The snippet files are
extracted from a verified Phase-2 E2 bundle before compilation. The
single-file aggregator includes Phase-2 structure diagnostic snippets
\texttt{phase2\_sf\_rsd\_summary.tex} and \texttt{phase2\_sf\_fsigma8.tex},
plus Sigma-origin RG status snippets \texttt{phase2\_rg\_flow\_table.tex} /
\texttt{phase2\_rg\_pade\_fit.tex} in deterministic order.

